# Firebase CLI automatically loads apps/functions/.env during deploy and sends
# those values as plain Cloud Run environment variables.
#
# Keep deployed Functions runtime config out of .env. Values declared with
# defineSecret belong in apps/functions/.secret.local for local emulator runs
# and Firebase Functions secrets for deployed runtimes, even when they are
# non-secret configuration such as APP_STORAGE_BUCKET.
#
# Prefer per-command shell variables for one-off local-only experiment flags.
#
# Admin/operator access is now Firebase Auth custom-claim based. Seed dev roles
# with `npm run dev:seed-auth-roles`; do not add allowlist secrets here.
